{"tid":613683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老老柒柒，腳波先應該入玩具台","createTime":"2018-04-02T01:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T16:26:32.000Z","uid":110437,"like":23,"dislike":168,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"94f62eead4df213d565c714bc84f794c7a20a5eb","tid":613683,"uid":110437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T01:17:08.000Z","msg":"大部分正式嘅運動都係室內進行，例如籃球、保齡球、桌球、羽毛球。<br />\n<br />\n腳波之所以係室外正正就係唔所受重視。<br />\n<br />\n你諗下成大班人係到鳩跑追住個波，成場先入得個幾粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當你班波台廢物似係死雞撐飯蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當你睇下奧運會唔會特登為腳波起地方個答案已經好明顯 無乜討論空間<br />\n<br />\n連單車都有室內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  醒下啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b57c519f7ae0c34fd23527fc07585bed96998ed","tid":613683,"uid":82710,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"咁陳茂波呢"},{"pid":"30414ae8c130bdaa485e870548d9b5a336b4616e","tid":613683,"uid":110437,"like":15,"dislike":17,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"推翻唔到淨係放低負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話足波拎只係無腦跑狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地方夠大比佢地鳩跑就開心"},{"pid":"7d41651502334d59a77ef4266d305213d78a5e7f","tid":613683,"uid":113206,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"巴打我掩護你快d走<br />\n班波台死矮仔準備入場"},{"pid":"46f9fa83d448566ce032ecd96c2d1fe7fe660cf3","tid":613683,"uid":55879,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"你知唔知起一個草地足球場要幾錢<br />\n常識都冇既小學雞好難同你溝通倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88cba988cdf630de5ee5c139111f723e9352280","tid":613683,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b57c519f7ae0c34fd23527fc07585bed96998e